item.title: Ecclisial ::master/::pure ECO
item.dc:creator: @Elrick Elrick
item.description:
@Elrick wrote:

I mean this with as much respect as possible, but that list is horrifying.

EDIT: Seeing as OP was unhappy with my opinion, I will explain why this is a weird list and overall thread.

  1. You double post your link for some reason, but you decided not to edit your post and fix it
  2. Your spacing is different between most of your lists
  3. You leave random spacing between even your related subjects
  4. You only use the “-” at the beginning for about 10 of the 50 listed things you wish to share
  5. You have quite a lot of spelling errors in your post, most of which are rudimentary words that appear in Runescape all around
  6. Your images do not present anything new or original about your server, I would suggest showing the custom and original content of your server instead of things like meaningless pking, as basically all servers have pking and damage markers.
